3
0:00:17.761,000 --> 0:00:2,000
what affects us most are the stories.

4
0:00:20.967,000 --> 0:00:23,000
So I want to begin with an everyday story.

5
0:00:24.179,000 --> 0:00:28,000
What is it really like to be a young woman in India?

6
0:00:28.702,000 --> 0:00:3,000
Now, I've spent the last 27 years of my life

7
0:00:30.974,000 --> 0:00:32,000
in India, lived in three small towns,

8
0:00:33.073,000 --> 0:00:34,000
two major cities,

9
0:00:34.889,000 --> 0:00:37,000
