33
0:01:53.085,000 --> 0:01:58,000
So throughout my life, I've seen women —

34
0:01:58.305,000 --> 0:01:59,000
family, friends, colleagues —

35
0:02:00.171,000 --> 0:02:02,000
live through these experiences,

36
0:02:02.964,000 --> 0:02:05,000
and they seldom talk about it.

37
0:02:06.137,000 --> 0:02:1,000
So in simple words, life in India is not easy.

38
0:02:10.777,000 --> 0:02:13,000
But today I'm not going to talk to you about this fear.

39
0:02:14.295,000 --> 0:02:15,000
