41
0:02:20.427,000 --> 0:02:23,000
So, what happened one night in December 2012

42
0:02:23.93,000 --> 0:02:24,000
changed my life.

43
0:02:25.704,000 --> 0:02:28,000
So a young girl, a 23-year-old student,

44
0:02:29,000 --> 0:02:33,000
boarded a bus in Delhi with her male friend.

45
0:02:33.904,000 --> 0:02:35,000
