54
0:02:58,000 --> 0:03:01,000
and knocked unconscious.

55
0:03:01.577,000 --> 0:03:05,000
She died on the 29th of December.

56
0:03:05.761,000 --> 0:03:06,000
And at a time when most of us here

57
0:03:07.739,000 --> 0:03:09,000
were preparing to welcome the new year,

58
0:03:10.242,000 --> 0:03:13,000
India plunged into darkness.

59
0:03:13.479,000 --> 0:03:16,000
For the first time in our history,

60
0:03:16.645,000 --> 0:03:18,000
men and women in Indian cities

61
0:03:18.823,000 --> 0:03:2,000
woke up to the horrific truth

62
0:03:21.014,000 --> 0:03:24,000
about the true state of women in the country.

63
0:03:24.536,000 --> 0:03:26,000
Now, like many other young women,

64
0:03:26.955,000 --> 0:03:28,000
I was absolutely terrified.

65
0:03:29.149,000 --> 0:03:3,000
I couldn't believe that something like this

66
0:03:30.416,000 --> 0:03:33,000
could happen in a national capital.

67
0:03:33.591,000 --> 0:03:35,000
I was angry and I was frustrated,

68
0:03:36.144,000 --> 0:03:4,000
but most of all, I felt utterly, completely helpless.

69
0:03:40.247,000 --> 0:03:42,000
But really, what do you do, right?

70
0:03:42.388,000 --> 0:03:44,000
Some write blogs, some ignore it,

71
0:03:44.413,000 --> 0:03:45,000
some join protests.

72
0:03:46.145,000 --> 0:03:48,000
I did all of it. In fact, that was what everyone was doing

73
0:03:48.71,000 --> 0:03:49,000
two years ago.

74
0:03:50.388,000 --> 0:03:52,000
So the media was filled with stories about

75
0:03:53.367,000 --> 0:03:54,000
all the horrific deeds

76
0:03:55.133,000 --> 0:03:57,000
that Indian men are capable of.

77
0:03:57.237,000 --> 0:03:58,000
They were compared to animals,

78
0:03:58.472,000 --> 0:04:,000
sexually repressed beasts.

79
0:04:00.659,000 --> 0:04:04,000
In fact, so alien and unthinkable was this event

80
0:04:04.663,000 --> 0:04:05,000
in an Indian mind

81
0:04:05.977,000 --> 0:04:07,000
that the response from the Indian media,

82
0:04:08.393,000 --> 0:04:11,000
public and politicians proved one point:

83
0:04:12.3,000 --> 0:04:13,000
No one knew what to do.

84
0:04:14.179,000 --> 0:04:16,000
And no one wanted to be responsible for it.

85
0:04:16.776,000 --> 0:04:18,000
In fact, these were a few insensitive comments

86
0:04:19.26,000 --> 0:04:2,000
which were made in the media

87
0:04:20.441,000 --> 0:04:22,000
by prominent people

88
0:04:22.468,000 --> 0:04:26,000
in response to sexual violence against women in general.

89
0:04:26.624,000 --> 0:04:29,000
So the first one is made by a member of parliament,

90
0:04:29.826,000 --> 0:04:32,000
the second one is made by a spiritual leader,

91
0:04:33.219,000 --> 0:04:35,000
and the third one was actually the defendants' lawyer

92
0:04:35.93,000 --> 0:04:36,000
when the girl was fighting for her life

93
0:04:37.776,000 --> 0:04:39,000
and she passed away.

94
0:04:40.63,000 --> 0:04:43,000
Now, as a woman watching this day after day,

95
0:04:44.483,000 --> 0:04:45,000
I was tired.

96
0:04:46.283,000 --> 0:04:47,000
So as a writer and gender activist,

97
0:04:47.927,000 --> 0:04:5,000
I have written extensively on women,

98
0:04:51.176,000 --> 0:04:53,000
but this time, I realized it was different,

99
0:04:53.822,000 --> 0:04:54,000
because a part of me realized

100
0:04:55.403,000 --> 0:04:57,000
I was a part of that young woman too,

101
0:04:57.751,000 --> 0:04:59,000
and I decided I wanted to change this.

102
0:04:59.929,000 --> 0:05:03,000
So I did something spontaneous, hasty.

103
0:05:03.96,000 --> 0:05:05,000
I logged on to a citizen journalism platform

104
0:05:06.506,000 --> 0:05:07,000
called iReport,

105
0:05:07.962,000 --> 0:05:09,000
