157
0:07:25.14,000 --> 0:07:27,000
and I noticed there was a link

158
0:07:27.183,000 --> 0:07:28,000
that was being shared by my friends.

159
0:07:28.856,000 --> 0:07:3,000
I clicked on the link; it led me back

160
0:07:31.039,000 --> 0:07:35,000
to a report uploaded by an American girl

161
0:07:35.114,000 --> 0:07:37,000
called Michaela Cross.

162
0:07:37.322,000 --> 0:07:38,000
The report was titled,

163
0:07:38.71,000 --> 0:07:41,000
"India: The story you never wanted to hear."

164
0:07:41.951,000 --> 0:07:44,000
And in this report, she recounted her firsthand

165
0:07:45.096,000 --> 0:07:48,000
account of facing sexual harassment in India.

166
0:07:48.796,000 --> 0:07:51,000
She wrote, "There is no way to prepare for the eyes,

167
0:07:52.763,000 --> 0:07:54,000
