175
0:08:14.64,000 --> 0:08:16,000
She said she was stalked, groped,

176
0:08:16.656,000 --> 0:08:17,000
and masturbated at.

177
0:08:18.253,000 --> 0:08:2,000
Now, late that evening, the report went viral.

178
0:08:20.692,000 --> 0:08:23,000
